Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been sitting in that seat since we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:20.66,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(170,0)}Takahata Kyouko (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She sure has.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been two hours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, confide in me if you would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that great detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:00:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I just got a call from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone has died at my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers dance to the piano's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two people face-to-face is a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's case is pretty troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this crime that cannot be proven?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased was Soejima Itsurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 27 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the husband of Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, whose sister,\NTakahata Kyouko, is the owner of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are... a fallen chandelier and a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the gun accidentally went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to our surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you doing, Chiba!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soejima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was actually Detective Chiba's friend back in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His shotgun suddenly discharged, causing the\Nchandelier to fall and crash on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the estimated time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Approximately an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He entered her house by himself while she was out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Consumed alcohol to the point of getting drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grabbed the shotgun from the cabinet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Loaded up his gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And played with it until it went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Itsurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That something like this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:05:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the business which Itsurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} started turned\Nout to be a blunder, and he was deep in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he caused my little sister Shiori to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, he continued drinking and\Ncaused more trouble for those around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When my sister died of illness half a year\Nago, his drinking problem worsened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even went to the fitness club and\Nshooting range I showed him, drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lemme go! I said let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, the club expelled him, and his gun license was revoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, it looks like he wanted to get his hands on my guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why he snuck into your house when\Nyou were out, and ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that he was a drunkard... and he even consulted me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, he said he was going to quit... drinking alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to quit, but he just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had heard about the incident at the shooting range.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he vowed to me, and said he wouldn't touch a gun ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was blinded by alcohol and simply forgot about his vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he saw these delicious dishes lying around\Nhere, I bet he'd start to crave a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that these dishes all go well with alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, a brat like you shouldn't talk like you know about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He apparently raided my fridge for dishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm responsible for this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what we meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, we're interfering with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where are the keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she was out, how did this man get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see any traces of the windows or doors being forced open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He carried a spare key, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't see any spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And not only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see this man's wallet or cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The spare key is outside the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had let him know where I hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about for your cabinet with shotgun and shells?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I locked the doors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, it's rusted and the locks are not working so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's like this, anyone can easily open the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, an insecure cabinet such as that doesn't meet\Nthe requisites for the metropolitan firearm storage law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be prepared for a revocation of your license and any applicable fines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But thinking backwards, this may be what she had hoped for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of being held responsible for a person's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for this case, we'll deem it an accident and let the precinct handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's investigate this a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba, calm yourself down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an accident no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go outside and cool down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's understandable to react like that when your friend dies, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what were you doing at the cafe terrace?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For over two hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you waiting for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't waiting for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You go cool yourself down too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That... is from Soejima's cellphone strap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's the same strap Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} had before her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there weren't any cellphones at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, can you tell me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soejima's personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it came to sports, I was only good at judo, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was good at all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, at the same time, he couldn't really handle pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd been relieving his stress from work by drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the trouble he caused wasn't just\Nat the shooting range and the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go check out those incidents, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With some luck, maybe we can uncover some new facts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During our investigation, we uncovered\Nmore of his troublesome incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Driving under the influence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for the guard rail, his car\Nwould have gone over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would've been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, two months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was drunk and collapsed on the street in the cold winter weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would've frozen to death if he had been found any later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adding up these similar accidents and incidents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We get nine of them in the span of half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s death, Soejima became very depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that, for a while his consumption increased, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he would always say "I'm going to quit for real this time."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, just as he was getting better, he would relapse once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This happened over and over again for half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to quit, but he just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, he was a fortunate guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he was just her sister's husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the fines and compensation for the accidents he caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the condolence money and the role of a guarantor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were all taken care of by Kyouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who introduced him to the shooting range\Nand fitness club where he caused that trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the owner of the house with shotguns kept in an\Ninsecure cabinet, a house he could access using a spare key...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what "indirect intent" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indirect intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:32.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,INDIRECT INTENT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indirect intent refers to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person foreseeing that an action will\Nlikely result in a harmful outcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But disregards whether it's ensured or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And follows through with the action regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I'm surprised that you know something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard about it from Uncle Kogoro a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:12:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To foresee that a drunkard like Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nmight get himself killed under the influence...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet still allow him to drive a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inviting him to a shooting range and the swimming pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And leaving the house and allowed him to come, drink, and carry a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may die, or he may not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The possibility wasn't 100% but it wasn't zero, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the culprit bet on that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've borrowed the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We ought to tell Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the Inspector first...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, just hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the cellphone recharging indicator light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recharging?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, whose cellphone is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Soejima...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't want Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s cellphone data to vanish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he constantly recharged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room should've been vacant for at least half a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone entered this room recently and used the cellphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone really was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like they searched the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be a cat burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, they wouldn't have re-locked the door, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not long ago, I received a report from my transceiver...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that a cat burglar frequenting this\Nneighborhood was arrested at Beika Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something that looks like glitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you suspecting me of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calling us here all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit of this incident is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahata Kyouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Further explanations...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will be offered by Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, according to Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disregard what I said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do suspect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was you who killed Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I killed Itsurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This had been planned for over half a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, as long as the plan succeeds,\Nit doesn't matter how long it would take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a long-range murder plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A complete murder based on indirect intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knowing that Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was an alcoholic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You created numerous situations where\Nhe might get himself accidentally killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, all you had to do is wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like sitting in a cafe terrace, drinking tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like the plot for a movie or novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But do you have evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Evidence, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about time for the first piece of\Nevidence, no... witness, to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forced Beika Station to cooperate and brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? I heard nothing about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told me to assist Chiba with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:57.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This man is Nishitani Naoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:16:00.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(210,0)}Nishinani Naoya (37)\N{\fs13}Recurring Cat Burglar
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:00.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A recurring cat burglar who the Beika police arrested yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cat burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He snuck into this house yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And witnessed the incident taking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, tell us again about the testimony you gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was rummaging around on the second floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Itsurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's she up to, calling me all the way here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soon, he drank himself into a stupor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he took the gun out of the cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought it was bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every bit of it was being set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having her license revoked due to improper\Nstorage isn't even at our level of concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was actually a crime of murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that, it's merely that man's story!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you trust, me or that burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About where Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cellphone went...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you intrigued by it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were trying to find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That something was Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to delete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's she up to... calling me all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you used to call Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The data of your text message!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, you went into Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room\Nand tried to find the cellphone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's some impressive nail art.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, is every piece of them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhinestones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was dropped near Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the same, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As your nail decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the cellphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After pulling out the money from the wallet,\Nhe threw the whole pouch into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The data was damaged, impossible to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shame —\hyou couldn't get your evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:51.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But regardless, there wasn't such a message in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I was trying to find was not the message you sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cellphone, which you touched...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after her death, he still recharged the phone and cherished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To him, that was a symbol that Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man caused Shiori indescribable pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He deserved to die for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we finally know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About your true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you arresting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can neither arrest nor sentence you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A private detective's job merely is to find the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time I did find something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your sister's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiori's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just go ahead and pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably a message from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you read on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Itsurou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know we should hang onto each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I allowed illness to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I get well, promise me that you'll stand\Non your own feet and apologize to my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I know she'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she's the nicest in the world... my only big sister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiori...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before she died...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sent this message to Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I did was send you the saved message\Nstored inside Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I surprised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:21:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this was Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cellphone,\Nyou didn't think to check, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died of illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without knowing Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s true feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You began your plan to murder Soejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiori couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was supposed to hate that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soejima truly wanted to stand on his own feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't let anger control you, you could've seen it as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you've learned of Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s feelings, will\Nyou still turn a blind eye to what you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And lie to her constantly for the remainder of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiori...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahata Kyouko admitted to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, about what the law will decide regarding\Nher crime of "indirect intent"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't be revealed in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come to realize that splurging on alcohol is unhealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, by putting beer in front of me, I'm\Ntraining myself to resist the temptation...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Resisting too much will only stress your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Learn your lesson sometime, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Magatama
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:20.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look Forward to the Next Episode
